551/BYU-football-program-losing-anchor-of-its-office.html">Read the Deseret News story</a>.</p>
</div><div class="news-item omega"><a href="http://photo.byu.edu/pages/mark-philbrick-named-photographer-of-the-year" title=""><span class="img" data-alt="A BYU gymnast, soaked in water, throws her head back, creating beautiful water swirls" data-src="http://home.byu.edu/home/sites/default/files/SportsFeatures_MarkPhilbrick_01.jpg"></span></a><h3><a href="http://photo.byu.edu/pages/mark-philbrick-named-photographer-of-the-year" title="">Mark Philbrick named UPAA Photographer of the Year</a></h3><p>The <a href="http://www.upaa.org/annual-print-competition/2012-0">University Photographer&rsquo;s Association of America</a> has named BYU&rsquo;s Mark Philbrick the 2012 National Photographer of the Year. This is Philbrick&rsquo;s 7th POY Award, making him the winningest photographer in the history of the UPAA. <a href="http://photo.byu.edu/pages/mark-philbrick-named-photographer-of-the-year">See more on the BYU Photo blog</a>.</p>
